name: The Shelter (front window)
description:
This is the shelter, 2 doors and 2 windows, the perfect cube always hosting us for a cigarette.
Shelter is our destination when we start walking the path to Sahara. It's the ultimate point for watching, a little higher on the ground where we can see all parts of our village, and also the next village far away.
The village ends here, we stop to visit our shelter.
This is the other window you see in front of you, when you come inside from the entrance door. The front window is for checking if someone comes, a farmer or a stranger who knows us. In our tiny village, everyone recognizes a stranger.
